# Page scaffold

Every new `page.tsx` must include `HeroNavbar` and `Footer`:

```tsx
import HeroNavbar from "@/app/components/HeroNavbar";
import Footer from "@/app/components/Footer";

export default function PageName() {
  return (
    <main className="flex min-h-0 flex-1 flex-col">
      <HeroNavbar />

      {/* 84px top padding to clear the fixed navbar */}
      <div className="ds-container" style={{ paddingTop: 84 }}>
        {/* page content */}
      </div>

      <Footer />
    </main>
  );
}
```

- `<HeroNavbar />` goes directly inside `<main>`, before any content.
- `<Footer />` goes at the very end of `<main>`.
- The first `ds-container` needs `style={{ paddingTop: 84 }}` to clear the fixed navbar.
